## 5. Responsibility & Ownership Rules

* **Scheduled class IN** â†’ scheduled teacher owns.
* **Pass OUT** â†’ origin staff owns.
* **IN other destination** â†’ destination staff owns.
* Admin can always force change ownership (force close + reopen).

